            "title": "中東戰火最大贏家？非洲正成為全球能源新避風港",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"中東戰火最大贏家？非洲正成為全球能源新避風港\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fJuIlqiCLVq22oy4dvHRVg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/14979690-080a-11f1-bf4f-ceca2ee10c6e\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">中東戰火最大贏家？非洲正成為全球能源新避風港</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
